                    Experience stress that impacts their physical and mental wellbeing on a regular basis
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              {/* Mental Health Crisis */}
              <div className="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-indigo-50 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-purple-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300">
                <div className="text-center">
